title: Mental Health Awareness and Victor Cruz Interview
itunes:title: Mental Health Awareness and Victor Cruz Interview
description:
Today on the show we did “Power to the People” and had Rwenshaun and Dr. Jasper come on to educate us on mental health, which is good timing because May is Mental Health Awareness Month. We also had former Giants player Victor Cruz on the show who finally speaks on the infamous boat picture. Also Charlamagne gave Donkey of the Day to David Leavitt because he tried to make the explosion in Manchester a light situation.
